<li>Remembering [deceased’s name]'s kindness and laughter.  They will be deeply missed.</li>
<li> I'll always cherish the memories we made together with [deceased’s name].</li>
<li>My thoughts are with you; may fond memories bring you peace.</li>
<li>[Deceased's name] was such a special person. I'm here for you.</li>
<li>So sorry for your loss.  [Deceased's name] will be dearly missed.</li>
<li> May you find comfort in the love and support of those around you.</li>
